                                     {
                                         "text":  "### The History of a Theorem\n\nThe graph in this section is a visual proof—a mathematical argument that demonstrates the proposed concept is real (<htcite0>)—of the Pythagorean Theorem.\n\n#### Where is it?\n\nHave you ever asked yourself the following question?",
                                         "source":  [
                                                        {
                                                            "type":  1,
                                                            "uuid":  "fc17254b-5b9e-458b-8406-749d8fb6778a",
                                                            "text":  "Weisstein, Eric W.",
                                                            "page":  "",
                                                            "date_time":  {
                                                                              "type":  "gregory",
                                                                              "year":  "",
                                                                              "month":  "",
                                                                              "day":  ""
                                                                          }
                                                        }
                                                    ],
                                         "date_time":  null,
                                         "isTable":  false,
                                         "imgdesc":  "",
                                         "format":  "markdown",
                                         "PostMention":  ""
                                     },
                                     {
                                         "text":  "<center><div class=\"first_steps_reflection_parent\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection question_mark\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-brain\"></i></div><div class=\"first_steps_reflection\"><b>Reflection: Pythagorean Theorem</b><br /><br />Why do I need to learn the Pythagorean Theorem?</div></div></center></p>",
                                         "source":  [

                                                    ],
                                         "date_time":  null,
                                         "isTable":  false,
                                         "imgdesc":  "",
                                         "format":  "html",
                                         "PostMention":  ""
                                     },
                                     {
                                         "text":  "Nowadays, the Pythagorean Theorem is used daily by many professionals, often without people's knowledge. In this section, we make its use more visible to answer this reflection.\n\n#### The Discovery\n\nWhat we call the Pythagorean Theorem could not have been given that name when it was first discovered.\n\nWe will follow Dr. Daniel F. Mansfield, who uses the term \"triple diagonal\" to refer to the relationship between numbers that follow the same rule attributed to Pythagoras in ancient Babylonian texts, written in sexagesimal positional notation (<htcite0>).\n\nThe reasons for this are that Pythagoras could not have discovered something before he was born. Furthermore, despite the similarity between the values on the *Plimpton 322* tablet and the values obtained through trigonometry, it cannot be stated that the Babylonians used trigonometry in the same way as the Greeks and as we know it today. However, knowledge of the right triangle among the Babylonians is proven by the artifact *Si. 427*, housed in the Istanbul Archaeological Museum (<htcite1>).\n\nBesides the Babylonians, there are also records of the relationship between the values of a right triangle in India (<htcite2>).",
                                         "source":  [
                                                        {
                                                            "type":  1,
                                                            "uuid":  "b157e363-321b-4d0e-bf1c-72ac3a0a3f3f",
                                                            "text":  "Mansfield, D. F.",
                                                            "page":  "pp. 985 - 1003",
                                                            "date_time":  {
                                                                              "type":  "gregory",
                                                                              "year":  "2021",
                                                                              "month":  "",
                                                                              "day":  ""
                                                                          }
                                                        },
                                                        {
                                                            "type":  1,
                                                            "uuid":  "b157e363-321b-4d0e-bf1c-72ac3a0a3f3f",
                                                            "text":  "Mansfield, D. F.",
                                                            "page":  "pp. 985 - 1003",
                                                            "date_time":  {
                                                                              "type":  "gregory",
                                                                              "year":  "2021",
                                                                              "month":  "",
                                                                              "day":  ""
                                                                          }
                                                        },
                                                        {
                                                            "type":  1,
                                                            "uuid":  "f40bd766-4f57-4f9b-a715-dd75311cada5",
                                                            "text":  "Britannica, T. Editors of Encyclopaedia",
                                                            "page":  "",
                                                            "date_time":  {
                                                                              "type":  "gregory",
                                                                              "year":  "2024",
                                                                              "month":  "11",
                                                                              "day":  "03"
                                                                          }
                                                        }
                                                    ],
                                         "date_time":  null,
                                         "isTable":  false,
